message.content:
I need to identify which line item represents costs incurred to secure customer orders and deliver goods and services to customers.

Looking at the income statement, these costs typically include:
1. Cost of Goods Sold - The direct costs of producing goods sold by the company
2. Selling Expenses - Costs related to marketing, sales, and delivering products to customers

In this income statement, the line item that specifically relates to securing customer orders and delivering goods/services is "Selling Expenses" with a value of 319828.12.

```json
{"solution": {'value': '319828.12'}}
```
